&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is a technically strong accounting leader who has built and managed accounting functions at companies with both meaningful scale of physical inventory and subscription or SaaS revenue streams. This person thrives on building process, driving accuracy, and serving as the operational backbone of the finance organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
