&lt;li&gt;Identify and activate on real-time cultural moments, trends and conversations that create opportunities for the brand to show up in relevant, unexpected ways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the social team to surface audience insights, test messaging and creative hypotheses, and ensure social is integrated into broader campaign planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the retail marketing strategy for key partners including Amazon, Babylist and Target, translating brand messaging into programs that drive sell-in, sell-through and a consistent brand presence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and evaluate brand partnership opportunities that extend Nanit&#39;s reach and cultural relevance, and manage those relationships from concept through execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a strong pulse on competitive and cultural trends to inform campaign development and brand storytelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
